  "title": "Automation Vision System Developer | Kaki Bukit [ East ]",
  "description": "<ul><li><p><strong>Industry: Industrial Automation Manufacturer</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Role: Senior / Junior Vision Development Engineer</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Working Hours: Monday-Friday [8.30am - 5.45pm]</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Office Near Kaki Bukit MRT, Singapore</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Entitled to AWS & Medical Benefits</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Physical Interview at Office is Required For This Role</strong></p></li></ul></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li><p>Degree / Diploma in EEE/Software Engineering/Computer Science.</p></li><li><p><em><strong>This role will require to travel overseas for product training, exhibition at UAE, Thailand, China, Taiwan few times a year based on business needs. [ Must flexible & able to travel upon request ]</strong></em></p></li><li><p><strong>For Senior Position</strong> - More than 3 years working experience in vision application development with hardware selection and software implementation</p></li><li><p><strong>For Engineer Position</strong> – 1 year working experience in vision application development with hardware selection and software implementation</p></li><li><p>Experience in software programming using C# with Microsoft Visual Studio.</p></li><li><p>Experience in PC based software design and implementation in auto machine / equipment development will be an added advantage.</p></li><li><p>Experience in Microsoft C++ will be an added advantage.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Jobs Scope: </strong></p><ol><li><p>You are required to develop and maintain new and existing vision applications.</p></li><li><p>Key functions include requirement analysis, sample evaluation, hardware testing, image analysis, software design, coding, testing, integration, documentation and customer training.<br /><br />Attends for overseas business trip, product training and application exhibition in foreign country upon request.<br /></p></li></ol><p>#SCR-carson-cheong</p><p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p><p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p>",
